#. [campaign]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/_main.cfg:30
msgid ""
"This is the story of an age when the glory of Wesnoth had become but a "
"memory of days long past. The fugitive necromancer Gwiti Ha’atel is "
"determined to master the undead hordes and exact his revenge upon the "
"living. His dark journey unleashes waves of power that gradually engulf all "
"of Irdya...\n"
"\n"
"(Expert level, 7 scenarios of 9 completed.)"
msgstr ""
"Wesnoth の栄光が遠い追憶の中に消え去った時代の物語。逃亡した死霊術師 Gwiti "
"Ha’atel は、アンデッドの大軍団を支配し、生ける者達に復讐する事を決意した。彼"
"の暗い旅筋は、徐々に Irdya 全てを飲み込む力の波を解き放つ......\n"
"\n"
"（達人レベル、9 シナリオ中 7 シナリオ完了）"

#. [campaign]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/_main.cfg:41
msgid "Episode II: The Death March"
msgstr "エピソード II：死の行軍"

#. [campaign]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/_main.cfg:41
msgid ""
"At last, Gwiti’s evil forces launch their assault against Wesnoth. As the "
"mortals under his command plunge the kingdom and its people into darkness, "
"they turn to their final hope: the elven enchantress Elynia. Thus begins the "
"ultimate confrontation between light and darkness.\n"
"\n"
"(Expert level, 0 scenarios of 9 completed.)"
msgstr ""
"遂に Gwiti の邪悪な勢力が Wesnoth への攻撃を開始した。Gwiti の配下が王国のそ"
"の人々を闇へ陥れる中で、彼らは最後の望みをエルフの魔法使い Elynia へと託"
"す...... こうして、光と闇の最終的な対決が幕を開けるのであった。\n"
"\n"
"（達人レベル、9 シナリオ中 0 シナリオ完了）"

