#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/00_Overture.cfg:54
msgid "Your unlife ends here. By my hand, your evil is undone."
msgstr "お前の不死はここで終わり。私の手で、お前の邪悪は潰える。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/00_Overture.cfg:60
msgid ""
"I fall... but <i>you</i> shall live <i>forever</i>. I curse you, Elynia — "
"you shall watch as time itself destroys all you have wrought. You shall "
"witness this world wither and perish. Each of your beloved ones shall pass "
"in agony, until you rue the day you dared stand against me."
msgstr ""
"私は敗れた...... だが<i>お前</i>こそは<i>永遠に</i>生きるだろう。お前を呪う、"
"Elynia —— 時がお前の築いた全てを破壊するのを見よ。この世界が枯れ滅びるのを見"
"よ。お前の最も愛する者達が苦しみと共に過ぎ去るのを見よ...... お前が私に対峙し"
"た日を後悔するまで。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/00_Overture.cfg:66
msgid ""
"In the end, the weight of loss shall grant you an eternity of torment... "
"haha... ha..."
msgstr ""
"そして最後に、失ったモノの重さが永遠の苦しみを与えるであろう...... ハ"
"ハ...... ハ......"

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/00_Overture.cfg:74
msgid "Gwiti — your destruction is not yet at hand."
msgstr "Gwiti —— お前の破滅の時はまだ先だ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/00_Overture.cfg:104
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:234
msgid "..."
msgstr "......"

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/00_Overture.cfg:108
msgid "Awaken."
msgstr "目覚めよ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/00_Overture.cfg:118
msgid "Do I... still exist?"
msgstr "私は...... まだ存在している？"

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/00_Overture.cfg:121
msgid "The final ritual remains incomplete. The dark powers must be unleashed."
msgstr "最後の儀式がまだ不完全なままだ。闇の力を解き放て。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/00_Overture.cfg:125
msgid ""
"The time has come at last? Long have I yearned to hear your voice again."
msgstr ""
"遂にその時が来たのか？貴様の声をもう一度聞く日を、私は心待ちにしていた...... "
"長きに渡って。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/00_Overture.cfg:149
msgid "<i><b>Here and now, the revival begins.</b></i>"
msgstr "<i><b>今ここにて始る。今こそ復活を。</b></i>"

