#. [message]: speaker=Blucyn
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:186
msgid ""
"Look north! A huge army of orcs is moving here. It looks like they are "
"planning to attack the fortress."
msgstr ""
"北を見ろ！オークの大軍がここへ向かっている。奴らは要塞を攻撃する魂胆だ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:198
msgid "<i>Brother, are the preparations complete?</i>"
msgstr "<i>兄弟よ。準備は整ったか？</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:202
msgid ""
"<i>You need not remind me. Everything proceeds according to our design.</i>"
msgstr "<i>貴様がそれを言うのか？全ては我らの策の通りに進んでいるのだ。</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Blucyn
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:206
msgid "The fate of Wesnoth lies in our hands. To arms!"
msgstr "Wesnoth の運命は我らの行動次第だ。武器を取れ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:294
msgid ""
"At last, the time to perform the ritual has finally come. Now we may "
"transcend the boundaries of life and death... all shall bend to our will."
msgstr ""
"遂に儀式を行う時が来た。今、我らは生と死の境界を越え...... 全てを我らの意のま"
"まに屈服させる事ができる。"

#. [message]: type=Skeleton
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:386
msgid "Ugh... ugh... I was... once dead..."
msgstr "うぐっ... うぐっ... 私は... 一度死んだ..."

#. [message]: type=Ghost
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:391
msgid "Souls... I need... more souls..."
msgstr "魂が... 必要だ... より多くの..."

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:397
msgid "Flesh, bone, soul, and death. All of these we command..."
msgstr "肉、骨、魂、そして死。その全てが我らの手にあり......"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:405
msgid "... and resurrect to life."
msgstr "......そして蘇りへ導く。"

#. [message]: speaker=Blucyn
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:413
msgid ""
"What?! <i>You!</i> You have violated the most sacred of taboos. This evil "
"surpasses even that of the orcs!"
msgstr ""
"何...... <i>貴様！</i>お前達は最も邪悪な禁忌を犯した。この邪悪さは、オーク共"
"のそれすらも凌ぐ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Blucyn
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:418
msgid ""
"Call for reinforcements! We must purge not only the orcs, but all of them as "
"well."
msgstr "増援を！オークのみならず、奴ら全ての存在をも浄化する為に。"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:436
msgid "Defeat Blucyn"
msgstr "Blucyn を倒す"

#. [unit]: id=Gweodoc, type=Paladin
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:499
msgid "Gweodoc"
msgstr "Gweodoc"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweodoc
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:520
msgid ""
"Damn! We were too late to save him. But in the end, he left us enough time "
"to destroy the undead."
msgstr ""
"畜生！彼を救うには遅かった。だが最後に、彼はアンデッドを倒す為に十分な時間を"
"稼いでくれた。"

#. [message]: type=Paladin
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:527
msgid "Prepare to meet your doom, necromancers!"
msgstr "己が破滅を覚悟しろ、死霊術師よ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gadash
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:532
msgid ""
"Look how these humans turn on themselves. Now it will be even easier for us "
"to crush them!"
msgstr "見ろ、人間共が互いに争っておる。今こそ我らの攻撃の好機だ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:541
msgid "Brother, what course shall we take?"
msgstr "兄弟よ、我らはどの道を取る？"

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:545
msgid ""
"This land has grown too small for my ambitions. Too many vermin stand in my "
"path. I shall depart... but your journey ends here."
msgstr ""
"この領域は、我が野望の実現には狭すぎる。そして私を煩わせる虫共も多い。私は行"
"く...... だがお前の旅はここで終わる。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:569
msgid ""
"Foolish brother! Know that you are not the only one destined to survive!"
msgstr "愚かなる兄弟よ！生きる運命にあるのは己だけでない事を知れ。"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:579
msgid "Move Gwiti to the escape route"
msgstr "Gwiti を脱出路まで移動させる"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:600
msgid ""
"I cannot fall here! Soon I shall return with an army at my back, and you "
"shall all be destroyed!"
msgstr ""
"私はここでは倒れぬ！今に私は軍勢を引き連れて戻るだろう、貴様らを滅ぼす為に"
"な！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:616
msgid "Argh! Our lord shall have vengeance upon you all!"
msgstr "アーッ！我らの君主が必ず、お前達全てに復讐を遂げるだろう！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:629
msgid "Rise from the depths of death!"
msgstr "死の淵より甦れ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gadash
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:654
msgid "I... shall obey... master..."
msgstr "私は...... 従う...... ご主人......"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:658
msgid "Scout the enemy positions and create diversions. Now go!"
msgstr "敵の位置を探り、陽動をせよ。行け！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweodoc
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:694
msgid "After them! We must not let them escape!"
msgstr "奴らを追え！奴らを見逃す事はできん！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:719
msgid "You should never have let me fall. Without me, you are nothing."
msgstr "私を殺すとは愚かな。私が居なければお前は何もできまい。"

