#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:110
msgid "Rek Iceheart"
msgstr "Rek Iceheart"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:156
msgid "A sudden tempest seized the vessel bearing Gwiti and Nati."
msgstr "突如として荒々しい嵐が、Gwiti と Nati を乗せた船を襲った。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:161
msgid "The ship splintered apart."
msgstr "船体は木端微塵に砕け散った。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:166
msgid "Yet the brothers’ tale was not to end there."
msgstr "だが兄弟の物語が、ここで終わる事はなかった。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:205
msgid "Do I... still draw breath?"
msgstr "私は...... まだ息をしている？"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:220
msgid "I have washed ashore, it seems... but Nati is nowhere to be found."
msgstr "どうやら、私は海岸へ漂着したらしい...... Nati の姿は見当たらないが。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:250
msgid ""
"My shackles lie broken. Perhaps the dark gods have not wholly forsaken me."
msgstr "枷は砕け散っている。暗黒の神々は私を見放してはいなかったのだ。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [unit]: id=Arkal-Thil, type=Dark Adept
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:255
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:267
msgid "Arkal-Thil"
msgstr "Arkal-Thil"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:256
msgid "I sense the shadow of darkness within you..."
msgstr "あなたの内に漂う...... 闇の気配を感じる......"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:262
msgid "Who addresses me?"
msgstr "誰だ？私を見ているのは？"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:285
msgid "I am a sorcerer, Arkal-Thil by name."
msgstr "私は Arkal-Thil の名による魔術師です。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:289
msgid "You are a necromancer, like myself... are you not?"
msgstr "お前もまた私と同じ、死霊術師ではないか？"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:293
msgid ""
"Indeed. Will you be our salvation? These grounds once served as sanctuary "
"for our cult. But savage beasts descended upon us, devouring most of our "
"number. We lacked the strength to repel them."
msgstr ""
"その通りです。我らの救い手となってはくれませんか？以前、この地は我らの教団の"
"聖域でした。しかし獣共が襲来し、多くの同朋が喰らわれたのです。奴らを撃退する"
"力が我らにはありませんでした。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:297
msgid ""
"They await only destruction at my hands. Soon they shall serve me eternally "
"as undying warriors."
msgstr ""
"奴らを待つのは我が手による滅びのみ。やがて不死の戦士として永遠に私に仕える事"
"となろう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:302
msgid ""
"We are grateful, new master. We pledge ourselves to you. Now is the hour of "
"vengeance and bloodshed!"
msgstr ""
"感謝いたします、新たなる我が主よ。我らはあなたに忠誠を誓います。今こそ復讐と"
"血の流れる時だ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Xabrak
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:339
msgid ""
"Look there! The necromancer assails us with his skeletal legion! But "
"strange... we thought we had destroyed them all."
msgstr ""
"オイ、見ろ！死霊術師が骸骨を率いて攻めてくるぞ！しかし奇妙だな...... 皆喰っち"
"まったはずだが。"

#. [message]: speaker=Grakarat
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:343
msgid "How I relish crushing their bones! Let battle be joined!"
msgstr "骨を砕く快感が再び！今こそ戦いの時だ！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:374
msgid "Who languishes in this cage?"
msgstr "檻に囚われておるのは誰だ？"

#. [unit]: id=Gabtur, type=Death Squire
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:381
msgid "Gabtur"
msgstr "Gabtur"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:397
msgid "One of our brothers! They slew him once already!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gabtur
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:402
msgid ""
"Danger lurks here... This is the den of the savages who slew me and "
"imprisoned my spirit."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:407
msgid ""
"Gabtur, it is I! We have found a new master. Already most of the beasts lie "
"dead at our feet!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:412
msgid "Join my uprising. I shall grant you power beyond measure."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:431
msgid "Gwiti — you must not tarry. Your destiny beckons."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:435
msgid "What? Who dares speak to my very thoughts? Reveal yourself!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:439
msgid ""
"Your brother Nati also treads this land. You must confront him, for only one "
"Ha’atel shall survive this crucible."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:443
msgid "Impossible! I shall not be the one to fall!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:460
msgid "Death comes for all naga who dare stand in my path!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:470
msgid "I am... vanquished..."
msgstr "私は...... 敗れた......"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:486
msgid "Who lurks in the shadows?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gadash
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:500
msgid "Master... I return to you."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:504
msgid "How came you to this place?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gadash
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:509
msgid "I followed your final command faithfully."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:513
msgid ""
"You were scouting far from the battlefield when disaster struck. Is that "
"what you mean to tell me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gadash
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:518
msgid ""
"I sensed your dark power upon this shore. The journey to return to your side "
"was long, but now I stand ready to serve once more."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:527
msgid "The Wesnothians have discovered my escape! All is lost..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=03_Brother_Against_Brother
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:5
msgid "Brother Against Brother"
msgstr "兄弟対兄弟"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:33
msgid "Defeat your brother Nati Ha’atel"
msgstr "兄弟 Nati Ha’atel を倒す"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:115
msgid ""
"As the crimson light of dusk painted the horizon, Gwiti discovered his arch-"
"rival and brother, Nati, had already taken position nearby — their long-"
"standing animosity about to reach its inevitable conclusion."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:121
msgid ""
"Ah, loathed brother mine. Gaze well upon this setting sun, for it shall be "
"the last you shall witness in these lands."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:125
msgid ""
"These lands? Your ignorance betrays you more thoroughly than your words ever "
"could."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:129
msgid "You, who fled like a coward at Erzen, dare speak of ignorance?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:133
msgid ""
"Cease your hollow boasting. You are but a shadow of what I once deemed a "
"worthy opponent."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:137
msgid "I shall prove my power in the darkness... You shall fall."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:141
msgid ""
"I will crush you with all the might that has always set me apart. Flee now, "
"or be annihilated."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:165
msgid "Your scalp shall make a fitting trophy."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:169
msgid "Master, will you truly destroy your own brother?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:173
msgid ""
"Blood ties mean nothing when destiny calls. Would you hesitate in my place?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:177
msgid "... I suppose not, master."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:185
msgid "Your doom draws near!"
msgstr "お前の破滅は目の前だ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:196
msgid ""
"His forces are but a disorganized rabble, barely worth our concern. Our "
"victory is inevitable."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:200
msgid "As you command, let us see it through."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:205
msgid ""
"Face your brother, necromancer. Your true power lies not in blood, but in "
"the darkness you command."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:208
msgid "You again... Who are you, that speaks from the shadows?"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:210
msgid "One who knows the path of true power. Prove yourself worthy."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:218
msgid ""
"Witness your final moments, you miserable wretch. Know that it is only by my "
"mercy you still bask in the light of the sun. Before it sets, you shall meet "
"your end."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:222
msgid ""
"Let me remind you that even now, my undead legions march forth, eager to "
"embrace you in death. Your fate is sealed."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:233
msgid ""
"My foolish brother... Our destiny was written the moment we drew breath. You "
"merely prolong the inevitable."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:237
msgid ""
"Is that your final testament? I shall continue my vengeance against Wesnoth. "
"Prepare yourself for what comes after."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:241
msgid "It is over... I am doomed... I am undone."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:257
msgid "Burn to ash, all who stand in my path!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:270
msgid "Die, and be forgotten!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [floating_text]
#. [scenario]: id=04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:461
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:476
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:5
msgid "The Skull of Morgorath"
msgstr "Morgorath の頭蓋骨"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:33
msgid "Move Gwiti himself on all the monoliths"
msgstr "全ての石碑の上に Gwiti を移動させる"

#. [note]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:45
msgid "4 monoliths remaining."
msgstr "4 の石碑が残っています。"

#. [note]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:54
msgid "3 monoliths remaining."
msgstr "3 の石碑が残っています。"

#. [note]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:63
msgid "2 monoliths remaining."
msgstr "2 の石碑が残っています。"

#. [note]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:72
msgid "1 monolith remaining."
msgstr "1 の石碑が残っています。"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Karz Gholum
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:115
msgid "Karz Gholum"
msgstr "Karz Gholum"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Nakur Kimoni
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:165
msgid "Nakur Kimoni"
msgstr "Nakur Kimoni"

#. [unit]: type=Orcish Warrior, id=Isidal B'Tai
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:203
msgid "Isidal B’Tai"
msgstr "Isidal B’Tai"

#. [side]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:225
msgid "team_name^Morgorath"
msgstr "Morgorath"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:249
msgid ""
"As Gwiti marched along the rugged mountain path, he felt the tingling "
"presence of strange magic weaving through the air, guiding him onward."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:254
msgid "I sense that I am nearing the Skull of Morgorath..."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:256
msgid ""
"Indeed, you are close — but you must perform the ritual to claim your prize. "
"Through your own will and magic, you must awaken the power of the ancient "
"monoliths scattered throughout this land."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:326
msgid ""
"Without my magic, these monoliths remain dormant. Do not squander your time "
"in futile efforts."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:332
msgid ""
"I find it curious that you still hide in the shadows. Have you not the "
"courage to reveal yourself?"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:334
msgid ""
"The time for revelations has not yet come. Trust in the path that lies ahead."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:341
msgid "Are we certain this is the right path? Doubt gnaws at me."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:345
msgid ""
"I share your concern. Only time will tell if the master of the voice speaks "
"the truth or leads us astray..."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:352
msgid ""
"Doubt is a poison that clouds the mind. Embrace your destiny, for it is "
"intertwined with the very fabric of this land."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:355
msgid "I will not succumb to fear. The power I seek is within my grasp!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:359
msgid ""
"Let us hope that we are worthy of the challenges ahead. Our journey is "
"fraught with peril."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:361
msgid ""
"Remember, it is through trials that strength is forged. Prepare yourselves; "
"the monoliths await your call."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [floating_text]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:374
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:389
msgid "Memoirs of the Dawn"
msgstr "夜明けの回顧録"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:375
msgid ""
"<i>In ages past, our realm knew an epoch of unrivaled splendor. We dwelt in "
"eternal radiance, basking in the golden light of prosperity and glory. In "
"our hubris, we believed our dominion over all living things would endure "
"until the end of time itself. Yet fate proved otherwise, for those who "
"watched from above could not abide such pride.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>遠い昔の時代、我らが領域は比類なき輝きの時代を知っていた。我らは永遠の光明"
"の中に在り、繁栄と栄光の黄金の光の中で生きた。その傲慢さ故に、我らは全ての生"
"ける者への支配が時の果てまで続くと信じていた。だが運命は異なる道を示した。上"
"より見守る者達は、そのような慢心を容認できなかったのだ。</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [floating_text]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:403
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:418
msgid "Memoirs of the Fall"
msgstr "大堕落の回顧録"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:404
msgid ""
"<i>The Great War raged across eons, until at last we fell from grace. In "
"that cataclysmic hour, both life and void were rent asunder. My own essence "
"was scattered, my form unmade by divine decree, cast adrift from the realm "
"of being.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>大戦は永劫に渡って猛り狂い、遂に我らは恩寵より転落した。その激変の時、生命"
"も虚無も引き裂かれた。我が本質は散り散りとなり、神の裁きにより形すら失い、存"
"在の領域より追放されたのである。</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [floating_text]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:432
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:447
msgid "Leganoth"
msgstr "Leganoth"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:433
msgid ""
"<i>Yet a fragment of my will remained, sealed within an emissary who walks "
"the mortal realm. In them I placed a shard of my consciousness, and bestowed "
"the ancient knowledge to draw forth my essence from its celestial prison. "
"Upon this vessel of my purpose, I bestowed the name Leganoth.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>だが我が意志の欠片は、死すべき世界を歩む使者の中に封印されていた。我はその"
"者の中に我が意識の破片を宿し、天上の牢獄より我が本質を呼び覚ます古の知識を授"
"けた。我が目的を託したその器に、Leganoth の名を授けたのである。</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:462
msgid ""
"<i>And so I endure in timeless vigil, awaiting the hour when my sundered "
"form shall be made whole once more — when flesh, bone, and spirit shall "
"unite in harmony. Then shall I rise again as Sovereign of Shadow, to claim "
"my rightful dominion. The appointed time draws ever nearer... This truth "
"echoes through the void.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>かくして我は時を超えた見張りの中で耐え忍び、引き裂かれし我が姿が再び一つと"
"なる時を待ち続ける —— 肉と骨と魂が調和の中で結ばれる時を。その時こそ、我は影"
"の君主として再び立ち上がり、正当なる支配権を主張するであろう。定められし時は"
"刻一刻と近づいている...... この真実が虚無を通じて響き渡るのだ。</i>"

#. [then]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:494
msgid "Well done. At last, you have proven yourself to be the chosen one."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:519
msgid "The undead are upon us! To arms, brothers!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:523
msgid ""
"Orcs? It has been too long since I last faced you in battle at Erzen... "
"Soon, your corpses and souls shall litter this battlefield."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:534
msgid "I have fallen to the wicked undead! Avenge me, my kin!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:548
msgid "Dispatch a messenger! Inform our lord of our demise..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:558
msgid "Argh! I meet my end!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:613
