#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:198
msgid ""
"And so, Gwiti set his sights upon the Tower of Kaleon, where the greatest "
"magi of the age had once studied and guarded their arcane secrets."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:203
msgid ""
"If my memory serves, that structure in the distance must indeed be the Tower "
"of Kaleon. The ancient spells and knowledge stored within will soon be mine "
"— and with them, my power shall grow vast enough to crush Wesnoth."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Quirind
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:210
msgid ""
"A dark sorcerer draws near! Could it truly be the same one we cast out long "
"ago?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Quirind
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:214
msgid ""
"Accursed practitioner of death, know that we, the magi of Kaleon, guardians "
"of this tower, shall defend it to our final breath! Turn back now, or face "
"ruin."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lessalin
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:219
msgid "Fear not, Quirind. By ancient accord, the elves shall stand with you."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urind
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:223
msgid ""
"Vile conjurer, this ground is no place for your kind. Leave, or we shall "
"banish you to the abyss!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:227
msgid ""
