#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:106
msgid ""
"Following ancient signs, Gwiti and Arkal-Thil arrive at a cramped, shadowed "
"cave passage. Even their dark vision is limited by the oppressive gloom "
"surrounding them."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:115
msgid ""
"So, we’re finally here... the resting place of Crelanu’s tome, hidden beyond "
"these darkness."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:119
msgid ""
"It feels different, master — colder, and something... alive? This place "
"seems to push back against us."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:123
msgid ""
"The book is well hidden, indeed. But that only proves its worth. We will "
"claim it, and this place will tremble at our presence."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:140
msgid ""
"<i>At the far end of the cave, a massive stone wall marked with ancient "
"runes blocks the way forward. The runes pulse faintly, their magical seals "
"still strong after centuries.</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:145
msgid ""
"Master, these runes seem to hold a protective spell. We may need to break it "
"piece by piece."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:149
msgid ""
"Then we must locate the guardians — no doubt they will appear the moment we "
"set foot on these sigils."
msgstr ""

