msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:207
msgid ""
"How amusing. Even in death, they cling to hollow oaths. Arkal-Thil, another "
"seal falls."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:240
msgid ""
"<i>With the last guardian vanquished, the runes on the wall fade. The "
"barrier crumbles, revealing a hidden chamber beyond — at its center, "
"surrounded by shallow pools, rests the Book of Crelanu upon a pedestal.</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:284
msgid ""
"<i>As Gwiti seizes the tome, tremors shake the cave, and shadows creep from "
"the depths. Feral creatures, bound to the tome’s defense, slink from the "
"pools and shadows.</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:310
